{"tid":1325042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"修例風波：元朗街頭播片指警濫用暴力　兩批市民爆衝突","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T18:08:51.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e3ea58e0421bf2984da1ebf1ae984f934ed555","tid":1325042,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS190716-14390-47-M&amp;d=1563289829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DONS190716-14390-47-M%26d%3D1563289829&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=111e89f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS190716-14390-47-M&amp;d=1563289829</a><br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》引發連串風波，今晚（16日）8時許，有市民在元朗鳳攸街休憩公園，播放連日來警員與示威者衝突的影片，指警方濫用暴力。期間引起另一批人士不滿，圍堵阻止，雙方爆發衝突，從市民拍攝的短片顯示，當時有不少人衝出馬路，有人更在行人路揮拳毆打，一時間喊聲震天，另有大批市民圍觀。其後，衝突雙方在街頭各自佔據一邊對峙，互相對罵，情況頗為混亂。警方於晚上9時許接報，派大批警員持盾牌到場，但現場已恢復平靜，部分人亦散去。不過，警方恐防再發生衝突，繼續留在現場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190716/photo/bkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190716230540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190716%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190716230540&h=a227af6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190716/photo/bkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190716230540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190716%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190716230540&h=121afd3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190716/photo/bkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_06b.jpg?20190716230540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190716%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20190716230540&h=cb213131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190716/photo/bkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_07b.jpg?20190716230540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190716%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190716220555250-0716_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20190716230540&h=4a045416&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e43750cb76ce3c3ba687d27d79307af22613d2a","tid":1325042,"uid":66208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721要人！！！721要人！！！721要人！！！721要人！！！721要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323956</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa195d90a6281f65965f5ef9253bdc40999a197b","tid":1325042,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"做乜撚"}]}